    6. `ledgers/exit-ledger.md` written — cumulative r2 state: all 20 entries' final disposition; cluster-wise summary (HIGH / MED / LOW); Coverlet baseline % cross-reference; Phase 4 deliverable cross-references; r3 scope recommendation per D-06
    7. Final verification: TASK-INDEX.md fully ✅; no critical issues; cleanup complete

    Project ready for shutdown.
  </goal>

